{
  "video_id": "GZadCj8O1-0",
  "title": "The $8 billion iPod | Rob Reid",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "The recent debate over copyright laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "like SOPA in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "and the ACTA agreement in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "has been very emotional."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "And I think some dispassionate, quantitative reasoning"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "could really bring a great deal to the debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d therefore like to propose"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "that we employ, we enlist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "the cutting edge field of copyright math"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "whenever we approach this subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "For instance, just recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "the Motion Picture Association revealed"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "that our economy loses 58 billion dollars a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "to copyright theft."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "Now rather than just argue about this number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "a copyright mathematician will analyze it"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;ll soon discover that this money"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "could stretch from this auditorium"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "all the way across Ocean Boulevard"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "to the Westin, and then to Mars ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "... if we use pennies."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "Now this is obviously a powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "some might say dangerously powerful, insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also a morally important one."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "Because this isn&#39;t just the hypothetical retail value"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "of some pirated movies that we&#39;re talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "but this is actual economic losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "This is the equivalent"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "to the entire American corn crop failing"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "along with all of our fruit crops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "as well as wheat, tobacco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "rice, sorghum --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "whatever sorghum is -- losing sorghum."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "But identifying the actual losses to the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "is almost impossible to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "unless we use copyright math."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "Now music revenues are down by about eight billion dollars a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "since Napster first came on the scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s a chunk of what we&#39;re looking for."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "But total movie revenues"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "across theaters, home video and pay-per-view are up."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "And TV, satellite and cable revenues are way up."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Other content markets like book publishing and radio"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "are also up."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "So this small missing chunk here"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "is puzzling."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "Since the big content markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "have grown in line with historic norms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not additional growth that piracy has prevented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "but copyright math tells us"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "it must therefore be foregone growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "in a market that has no historic norms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "one that didn&#39;t exist in the 90&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re looking at here"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "is the insidious cost of ringtone piracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "50 billion dollars of it a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "which is enough, at 30 seconds a ringtone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "that could stretch from here"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "to Neanderthal times."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "I have Excel."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "The movie folks also tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "that our economy loses"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "over 370,000 jobs to content theft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "which is quite a lot when you consider that, back in &#39;98,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "the Bureau of Labor Statistics indicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "that the motion picture and video industries"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "were employing 270,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "Other data has the music industry at about 45,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "And so the job losses that came with the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "and all that content theft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "have therefore left us with negative employment in our content industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "And this is just one of the many mind-blowing statistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "that copyright mathematicians have to deal with every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "And some people think that string theory is tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "Now this is a key number from the copyright mathematicians&#39; toolkit."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the precise amount of harm"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "that comes to media companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "whenever a single copyrighted song or movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "gets pirated."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "Hollywood and Congress derived this number mathematically"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "back when they last sat down to improve copyright damages"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "and made this law."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "Some people think this number&#39;s a little bit large,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "but copyright mathematicians who are media lobby experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "are merely surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "that it doesn&#39;t get compounded for inflation every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "Now when this law first passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s hottest MP3 player could hold just 10 songs."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "And it was a big Christmas hit."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "Because what little hoodlum wouldn&#39;t want"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "a million and a half bucks-worth of stolen goods in his pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "These days an iPod Classic can hold 40,000 songs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "which is to say eight billion dollars-worth"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "of stolen media."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "Or about 75,000 jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "Now you might find copyright math strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s because it&#39;s a field"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s best left to experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s it for now."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "I hope you&#39;ll join me next time"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "when I will be making an equally scientific and fact-based inquiry"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "into the cost of alien music piracy to he American economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}